WEBVTT

00:10:59.442 --> 00:11:01.695
double-checking the information,

00:11:01.695 --> 00:11:06.078
and looking also at 
the metadata of the material.

00:11:06.078 --> 00:11:09.197
Now, the fourth and the most
important thing I learned

00:11:09.197 --> 00:11:13.466
is how you use images 
to create a positive change.

00:11:14.450 --> 00:11:16.299
To have an effect,

00:11:16.299 --> 00:11:20.886
the key thing is how you use the material.

00:11:20.886 --> 00:11:23.404
Today, we're working
with hundreds of activists

00:11:23.404 --> 00:11:24.953
filming undercover.

00:11:24.953 --> 00:11:28.055
We work with them both to understand 
the situation on the ground

00:11:28.055 --> 00:11:31.045
and which images 
are missing to describe it,